data.description: A must see this stunning house with four bedrooms, two bathrooms, you will immediately notice the island and the Kitchen skylight that floods the home with abundance of natural light that creating a warm atmosphere. Enjoy the convenience of a built-in pest control system. The concept design seamlessly connects the living room, kitchen, and dining area making it perfect for entertaining. The recently replaced microwave and fresh coat of paint all throughout the home. Also, the extended covered patio, oversized backyard provides plenty of room for kids to play. Additionally, both the front and back yards are equipped with sprinkler systems. Residents have access to a sparkling pool and playground. Enjoy the nice cul -de-sac when you are setting on your cover front porch. You will have a HOME WARRANT for the first year up to $800.00. Just 0.5 mile from I 20- and 5-minutes frow downtown Ft Worth and major hospitals, commuting is a breeze.
